properties.name: Chloe's Coffee
properties.description: Posted by Kentlands    244 Main St. Gaithersburg, MD 20878To us, a coffee shop is all about community; both the neighborhoods we call home, and the community we all create together inside the café. This community can present itself in many ways, from the crowd gathered every Friday to hear live music by local artists, to something as simple as a sharing the comics section of your newspaper. As a young, independent business, we depend on our community, and we will strive to serve it for years to come.
